        {
          "character": "花荣",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "义旗指处人皆服，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "板斧双劈神鬼惊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "智多星吴用，"
        },
        {
          "character": "林冲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺豹子头林冲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "花荣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺小李广花荣，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱黑旋风李逵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日大哥升帐，我等两厢伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（大吹场。四龙套、四下手、宋江同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "点绛唇",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "水泊英豪，替天行道，兵符抱，胸藏韬略，威名四海遥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "义胆忠肝盖世无，心怀报国有良图。他年若遂凌云志，笑煞黄巢非丈夫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥在上，我等参拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位兄弟少礼，站立两厢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，及时雨宋江。只因杀了阎婆惜，逃上梁山。蒙众家兄妹，推我为山寨之主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前日探子报到，有神州总制王宏，新得一将，名唤赛金刚任原，英雄无敌。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "高搭擂台，夸下海口，要打尽天下英雄好汉。百日完满，就要带兵平定俺梁山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也曾命燕青前去打探。等他到来，便知分晓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（燕青上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "燕青",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打听不平事，报与大哥知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "燕青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少礼。我命你去至神州，打探任原之事如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "燕青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小弟奉了大哥之令，去至神州。果然有个任原，夸下海口，卖下浪言，摆设擂"
        },
        {
          "character": "燕青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "台，百日完满，就要起兵剿我梁山。那时小弟，要想上得擂台，将那厮打倒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "燕青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奈无大哥将令，不敢造次。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "竟有这等之事？待咱去到神州，上得擂台，将那厮活活擒来，方显俺的手段也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟休要卤莽，此事必须商议而行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，军师，此事当以何策处置？"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此事不难。待小弟遣众兄弟，潜往神州，先把任原打翻，那各路官兵，就不敢"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正眼觑我梁山也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此就请军师传令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，列位弟兄，哪位愿到神州，将任原打倒？忠义堂挂红领赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "燕青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺燕青愿往神州，若不将任原打下擂台，誓不为人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好！燕青听令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "燕青将，手段强，"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "神拿七十二，敢夸张。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得胜回山，名播扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此番去往神州府"
        },
        {
          "character": "燕青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（燕青下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "燕青虽然武艺高强，但是他一人，恐怕独力难支。谁人愿去帮助者，一同挂红"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位哥哥在上，也不是俺李逵夸口：此番俺去到擂台，若不将那厮做汤羊儿一"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "般，一只手揪住他脑袋，一只手拎着他的鸾带，擒上山来，捽在这忠义堂上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听凭二位哥哥发落，俺也誓不为人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好！李逵听令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黑旋风，甚凶勇，"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两柄板斧染腥红。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果是英雄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下山去好一似黑煞神"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李逵下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花荣、林冲听令。那王宏兵强马壮，他二人若打倒任原，岂肯干休必然有一场"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "厮杀。你二人可扮做客商模样，潜往神州，暗地帮助他成功者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有任原，太夸张，"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拔山举鼎，号金刚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "搅得他地乱天荒。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦明、王英暗同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "花荣、林冲",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（花荣、林冲同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦明、王英听令。你二人可扮做挑担脚夫，混入城中，暗地接应者。你二人呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猛如虎，貌似狼，"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乔装结束气昂昂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管叫他，无计猖狂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "饶你有官兵千百万"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦明"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（秦明、王英同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传女将们上堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "女将上堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（顾大嫂、孙二娘、扈三娘同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "顾大嫂、孙二娘、扈三娘",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥在上，我等参见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军师有差。"
        },
        {
          "character": "顾大嫂、孙二娘、扈三娘",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见军师。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众女将听令：你等可扮作乞婆，混入神州，接应众弟兄者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "女将们，快登程，"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去往神州护燕青。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方显梁山娘子军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若得成功回山转"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "顾大嫂"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "吹腔",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孙二娘"
        },
        {
          "character": "扈三娘",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（顾大嫂、孙二娘、扈三娘同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传令已毕。命戴宗扮做公差，时迁扮做花子，来往打探消息者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 四下埋伏了牢笼计，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管叫他插翅也难飞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宋江 （尾声） 方显俺及时雨的威名，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天下知。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（宋江、吴用同下。）"
        }
      ],
