    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "任原",
        "众人",
        "徒弟",
        "李逵"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四下手、四英雄、任原同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任原",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此擂台，一同上擂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任原",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "英雄上擂台，好汉两边排。打死不偿命，愿者请上来。大喊三声谁敢来，谁敢"
        },
        {
          "character": "任原",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徒弟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀师父：天气尚早，打擂的还靡有来呢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任原",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好生看守擂台。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徒弟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咋！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（任原下。四上手、花荣、林冲、燕青、李逵同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是擂台，果然有大言牌在此。待俺看来："
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打尽世间无敌手，争交天下我为魁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放你娘的屁！待我将它打碎了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徒弟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！你这黑脸贼，将我的大言牌打碎。你敢上来与我较量么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我先打死你个王八肏的！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李逵打倒徒弟。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徒弟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请师父。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（任原上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任原",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徒弟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打擂的来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任原",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闪开了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（任原起打，李逵败下。燕青上，起打，燕青打任原倒，李逵上，劈任原死。众人同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你为何将他劈死了？他那主帅闻知，怎肯干休？此祸闯得不小，你我同回山寨"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怕他娘的什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
